## Verification

1. **New content, click X** ‚Üí dialog appears with "Save as draft before closing?"
2. **Click "Save Draft"** ‚Üí draft saved, editor closes, draft appears in `/home/drafts`
3. **Click "Discard"** ‚Üí editor closes, no draft created, images cleaned up
4. **Existing draft with changes, click X** ‚Üí dialog appears with "Save changes before closing?"
5. **Click "Save Draft"** ‚Üí changes saved to existing draft, editor closes
6. **No content or no changes, click X** ‚Üí editor closes immediately (no dialog)
7. **After publish, click X** ‚Üí editor already closed by publish flow (no dialog)
